  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a lash of lightning energy that strikes at one creature of your choice that you can see within 15 feet of you. The target must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be pulled up to 10 feet in a straight line toward you and then take [[/r 1d8]] lightning damage if it is within 5 feet of you.</p><h3>At Higher Levels</h3><p>This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level ([[/r 2d8]]), 11th level ([[/r 3d8]]), and 17th level ([[/r 4d8]]).</p><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> Artificer, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard</p>",
